{"tid":1782184,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"蘋果A1: 警OT半年 十億公帑 毎人袋九萬","createTime":"2019-12-13T17:50:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-15T01:17:48.000Z","uid":240362,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d7ea41f4a4a6ab98b3ff2f09ccbb83374831c469","tid":1782184,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T17:50:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/80089061_10158399196077448_815377121416314880_n.jpg?_nc_cat=109&amp;_nc_ohc=zY4WZJaHHWIAQnAJ3lG1UbN1xYNo6dWCNVKGxrA9tkE2WIc7UkoHgp5AQ&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg10-1.fna&amp;oh=a6f95f2ed55c26f059b84a3b90cb13e7&amp;oe=5E870BAE\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F80089061_10158399196077448_815377121416314880_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D109%26_nc_ohc%3DzY4WZJaHHWIAQnAJ3lG1UbN1xYNo6dWCNVKGxrA9tkE2WIc7UkoHgp5AQ%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg10-1.fna%26oh%3Da6f95f2ed55c26f059b84a3b90cb13e7%26oe%3D5E870BAE&h=513a6582&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0afaf9560ef42f16db9130a6e66d5b5320bce7a2","tid":1782184,"uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T17:50:36.000Z","msg":"【A1頭條】持續逾半年的反修例運動，警方經常被批評藉故超時工作「呃OT」（逾時工作津貼），政府昨首次公佈警隊過去半年的超時補水高達9.5億元，月均領取人數達11,000人，意味平均每名警員可獲8.6萬元加班收入。但同為政府部門的港台新聞部卻被縮減資源、公立醫院醫生超時工作卻沒獲補水，做法被轟「大細超」。民主派議員怒轟警隊涉及無數宗濫暴、警黑勾結事件，如今要市民支付警隊OT費，實在不能接受，故勢要力阻暴警「無底洞呃OT」。"},{"pid":"3517d74ed3d6b7297734829602a77f9520887b9a","tid":1782184,"uid":229183,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T23:35:47.000Z","msg":"黑警無法無天大家都知架喇"},{"pid":"3cf7eb66f9102c89b9227a37381ddc5513dd5391","tid":1782184,"uid":30040,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T23:38:05.000Z","msg":"仲有202億買軍備呢，要全面軍政府係咁上下。"},{"pid":"4669872e67993d4e96e571a49c4903e82e96ec05","tid":1782184,"uid":24570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T00:15:18.000Z","msg":"市民埋單<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj